  "abstract": "The Board is publishing a final rule to amend Regulation C (Home Mortgage Disclosure) and the instructions that financial institutions [[Page 22224]] must use to comply with the annual reporting requirements under the regulation. The amendments conform Regulation C to reflect revisions adopted by the Board, the Office of the Comptroller of the Currency, the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation, and the Office of Thrift Supervision to their regulations implementing the Community Reinvestment Act",
